## hypotenuse of right angle triangle
import math
A = float(input("Enter the side A "))
B = float(input("Enter the side B "))
C=math.sqrt(pow(A,2) + pow(B,2))
print("Hypotenuse",C)

o/p:
Enter the side A 3
Enter the side B 4
Hypotenuse 5.0

